"{\"uid\": \"fansided.com-posts-2024-paris-olympics-mens-basketball-top-international-youth-players-to-watch\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Olympic basketball is not the place to get a look at blossoming young talent, usually.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 86, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is basketball's equivalent to the FIFA World Cup and the high stakes of such an event lead to most countries leaning on experienced hands, for better or for worse, to guide them to glory.\", \"from\": 87, \"to\": 277, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But talent trumps all, and plenty of scintillating youngsters could be on display at the 2024 Olympics in Paris.\", \"from\": 278, \"to\": 390, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 384, \"end\": 389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0457632917170935e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here are some of the most interesting names to watch under the age of 25, from the NBA and beyond.\", \"from\": 392, \"to\": 490, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 475, \"end\": 478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.652738745170818e-61, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Victor Wembanyama is... okay, he probably does not need an introduction.\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 564, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 492, \"end\": 509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Wembanyama\", \"score\": 0.9999841253316324, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Victor Wembanyama\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Wembanyama\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Wembanyama\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wembanyama is the NBA's reigning Rookie of the Year following his status as arguably the most hyped draft prospect of all time or at the very least the most hyped international draft prospect of all time.\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 769, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 583, \"end\": 586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.652738745170818e-61, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2024 Olympics in Paris will be Wembanyama's first time representing the French senior team at a truly prestigious, world-stage event.\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 908, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 792, \"end\": 797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0457632917170935e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 847, \"end\": 865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4002374967116868e-13, \"text\": \"French senior team\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With France hosting the Olympics, the stakes could not be higher for Wemby.\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 984, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 914, \"end\": 920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4628408485390117e-16, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Head coach Vincent Collet has started him alongside reigning Defensive Player of the Year Rudy Gobert, forming the greatest interior defense duo to ever play the game of basketball.\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 1166, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 996, \"end\": 1010, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vincent_Collet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vincent Collet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vincent_Collet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vincent_Collet\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While Wemby will be joined by Gobert and fellow NBA players Bilal Coulibaly, Evan Fournier, and Nico Batum, the pressure France has as hosts might be unfair for this squad.\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1340, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1216, \"end\": 1219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.652738745170818e-61, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 1228, \"end\": 1233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bilal_ibn_Rabah\", \"score\": 0.999180265381789, \"rank\": 0.0008204071346547745, \"text\": \"Bilal\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bilal_ibn_Rabah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bilal_ibn_Rabah\"}, {\"begin\": 1245, \"end\": 1258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Fournier\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Evan Fournier\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Fournier\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Fournier\"}, {\"begin\": 1264, \"end\": 1268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nico\", \"score\": 0.7111652372398382, \"rank\": 0.4061428560842543, \"text\": \"Nico\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nico\"}, {\"begin\": 1269, \"end\": 1274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicolas_Batum\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7783796554059927e-30, \"text\": \"Batum\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicolas_Batum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicolas_Batum\"}, {\"begin\": 1289, \"end\": 1295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4628408485390117e-16, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Les Bleus will expect to compete for a gold medal which is understandable, but this French squad is more or less the same squad that did not qualify for the knockout rounds of the 2023 FIBA World Cup against inferior competition.\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1570, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1425, \"end\": 1437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.80705241731569e-17, \"text\": \"French squad\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France is still dependent on Fournier and former San Antonio Spur turned EuroLeague star and now aging veteran Nando De Colo for their backcourt.\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1716, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1571, \"end\": 1577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4628408485390117e-16, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1600, \"end\": 1608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Fournier\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1249580505107614e-17, \"text\": \"Fournier\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Fournier\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Fournier\"}, {\"begin\": 1624, \"end\": 1631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonio_Dawson\", \"score\": 0.999796920660328, \"rank\": 0.00020311801022162914, \"text\": \"Antonio\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonio_Dawson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonio_Dawson\"}, {\"begin\": 1644, \"end\": 1654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/EuroLeague\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.175284559643077e-26, \"text\": \"EuroLeague\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/EuroLeague\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/EuroLeague\"}, {\"begin\": 1682, \"end\": 1695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nando_de_Colo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nando De Colo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nando_de_Colo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nando_de_Colo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France has talent, but the balance is not perfect.\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1767, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1717, \"end\": 1723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4628408485390117e-16, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Drawn into Group B with Germany, Brazil, and Japan, France should advance to the quarterfinals with relative comfort but the knockout stages could pose a challenge.\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1933, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1780, \"end\": 1787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2014_FIFA_World_Cup_Group_B\", \"score\": 0.999996299918645, \"rank\": 3.3115227561236185e-06, \"text\": \"Group B\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2014_FIFA_World_Cup_Group_B\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2014_FIFA_World_Cup_Group_B\"}, {\"begin\": 1793, \"end\": 1800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999754436, \"rank\": 2.4200945028265845e-11, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1802, \"end\": 1808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999929577825, \"rank\": 7.04180994063887e-09, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1814, \"end\": 1819, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999909517764617, \"rank\": 5.810148777439064e-06, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1821, \"end\": 1827, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4628408485390117e-16, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wemby is worthy of any and all pressure placed on him, but a disappointing performance from France should come as a surprise to no one.\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 2069, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2026, \"end\": 2032, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4628408485390117e-16, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For 2028, he could be joined by Zaccharie Risacher, Alex Sarr, and Nolan Traore.\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2150, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2122, \"end\": 2126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Russo\", \"score\": 0.9989991678129533, \"rank\": 0.0006387461087746355, \"text\": \"Alex\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Russo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Russo\"}, {\"begin\": 2137, \"end\": 2142, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Smith\", \"score\": 0.9999999961846697, \"rank\": 3.815340992220347e-09, \"text\": \"Nolan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Smith\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A young core that fits brilliantly and will be more than capable of going toe-to-toe with Team USA and anyone who dare challenge them.\", \"from\": 2151, \"to\": 2285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2241, \"end\": 2249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.392239393189099e-30, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Have high expectations for Wemby this summer, but do not be overly critical either.\", \"from\": 2286, \"to\": 2369, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Coming off an impressive rookie season for the Washington Wizards, Coulibaly will lurk in the shadows of Wemby at the 2024 Paris Olympics but could be the difference maker for this squads ceiling.\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2567, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2418, \"end\": 2436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Wizards\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1052211856184354e-90, \"text\": \"Washington Wizards\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Wizards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Wizards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If Coulibaly can deliver an A+ performance, Les Bleus have a chance to push for gold.\", \"from\": 2568, \"to\": 2653, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Similar to Wemby, Coulibaly should not be expected to deliver the type of performance that lifts France's overall ability to win the gold medal but it is something to watch.\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2828, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2752, \"end\": 2758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4628408485390117e-16, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We already know Coulibaly is a lockdown perimeter defender who, alongside Gobert, Wembanyama, and veteran Batum could form arguably the most intimidating defensive unit international basketball has ever seen.\", \"from\": 2829, \"to\": 3037, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2935, \"end\": 2940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicolas_Batum\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7783796554059927e-30, \"text\": \"Batum\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicolas_Batum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicolas_Batum\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France can and should lean into their defense at this tournament, it is arguably the best at the Olympics when they have their best five-man unit out there.\", \"from\": 3038, \"to\": 3194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3038, \"end\": 3044, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4628408485390117e-16, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes, even better than Team USA's.\", \"from\": 3195, \"to\": 3228, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The other end of the floor is where a strong Coulibaly performance this summer could change everything.\", \"from\": 3230, \"to\": 3333, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Coulibaly has not been the most consistent offensive player so far in his career and this is unsurprising for everyone who watched him as a prospect.\", \"from\": 3334, \"to\": 3483, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His on-ball skills left a decent amount to be desired, especially in the half-court, but some hot shooting and occasional self-creation could buoy this occasionally stagnant French offense.\", \"from\": 3484, \"to\": 3673, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3658, \"end\": 3664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999825695349768, \"rank\": 1.725986249217614e-05, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Coulibaly will turn 20 a day before the Olympics begin and France plays their first game, he should not be expected to be a savior for their gold medal dreams but he could be.\", \"from\": 3675, \"to\": 3850, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3734, \"end\": 3740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4628408485390117e-16, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That much is true.\", \"from\": 3851, \"to\": 3869, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Spain's golden generation of basketball is behind them.\", \"from\": 3871, \"to\": 3926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3871, \"end\": 3876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.249147203236097e-15, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Gasol brothers are gone, and the Hernangomez brothers are nowhere near the potential replacement many Spainards hoped they could be.\", \"from\": 3927, \"to\": 4063, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3964, \"end\": 3975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Willy_Hernang\\u00f3mez\", \"score\": 0.9943891044544022, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hernangomez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Willy_Hernang\\u00f3mez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Willy_Hernang\\u00f3mez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While Spain carries a clear amount of basketball pedigree on the old continent, their squad for Paris 2024 features two NBA players from last season: Usman Garuba and Santi Aldama.\", \"from\": 4064, \"to\": 4244, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4070, \"end\": 4075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.249147203236097e-15, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 4160, \"end\": 4170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0179098489141867e-25, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 4184, \"end\": 4187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.652738745170818e-61, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 4214, \"end\": 4226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usman_Garuba\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Usman Garuba\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usman_Garuba\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usman_Garuba\"}, {\"begin\": 4231, \"end\": 4243, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santi_Aldama\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Santi Aldama\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santi_Aldama\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santi_Aldama\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aldama is coming off a career-high season in, well, everything.\", \"from\": 4246, \"to\": 4309, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4246, \"end\": 4252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juan_Aldama\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.091477193658499e-19, \"text\": \"Aldama\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juan_Aldama\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juan_Aldama\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Points, rebounds, assists, minutes, etc.\", \"from\": 4310, \"to\": 4350, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You name it, he cleared a new benchmark.\", \"from\": 4351, \"to\": 4391, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Selected 30th overall by the Jazz in the 2021 NBA Draft and traded to the Grizzlies shortly thereafter, Aldama has provided great value to the Grizzlies and drawn comparisons to Lauri Markkanen following his improved play since his rookie season.\", \"from\": 4392, \"to\": 4638, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4433, \"end\": 4447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2021_NBA_draft\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2021 NBA Draft\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2021_NBA_draft\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2021_NBA_draft\"}, {\"begin\": 4496, \"end\": 4502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juan_Aldama\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.091477193658499e-19, \"text\": \"Aldama\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juan_Aldama\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juan_Aldama\"}, {\"begin\": 4576, \"end\": 4585, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lauri_Markkanen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.817593825395386e-17, \"text\": \"Markkanen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lauri_Markkanen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lauri_Markkanen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is eligible for a rookie extension, and a strong showing at the Olympics could be a step towards securing a healthy three-year deal should he want it.\", \"from\": 4639, \"to\": 4792, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Spain's squad is full of veterans, including Rudy Fernandez who will be retiring after the tournament which is a recor setting sixth Olympics appearance for the former Portland Trail Blazers wing, who will be looking to Aldama to provide a much needed scoring punch.\", \"from\": 4794, \"to\": 5060, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4794, \"end\": 4799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.249147203236097e-15, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 4839, \"end\": 4853, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rudy_Fernandez_(actor)\", \"score\": 0.5866134089603322, \"rank\": 0.6972789115645815, \"text\": \"Rudy Fernandez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rudy_Fernandez_(actor)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rudy_Fernandez_(actor)\"}, {\"begin\": 5014, \"end\": 5020, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juan_Aldama\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.091477193658499e-19, \"text\": \"Aldama\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juan_Aldama\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juan_Aldama\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He should have carte-blanche on the offensive end, and try to capitalize accordingly.\", \"from\": 5061, \"to\": 5146, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a weird way, Franz Wagner does not have much to prove for the German national team.\", \"from\": 5148, \"to\": 5234, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5164, \"end\": 5176, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Franz_Wagner_(basketball)\", \"score\": 0.9921778207483346, \"rank\": 0.00630666141111913, \"text\": \"Franz Wagner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Franz_Wagner_(basketball)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Franz_Wagner_(basketball)\"}, {\"begin\": 5213, \"end\": 5233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999996662154, \"rank\": 2.924643388372561e-10, \"text\": \"German national team\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alongside Dennis Schroder, he helped lead them to the gold medal at the 2023 FIBA World Cup.\", \"from\": 5235, \"to\": 5327, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5245, \"end\": 5260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dennis_Schr\\u00f6der\", \"score\": 0.9999999485871753, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dennis Schroder\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dennis_Schr\\u00f6der\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dennis_Schr\\u00f6der\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was the second gold medal in the country's history, with the previous one coming at Eurobasket 1993.\", \"from\": 5328, \"to\": 5433, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Essentially, Wagner has already done more for the German national team than Dirk Nowitzki (sorry, we love you, Dirk).\", \"from\": 5434, \"to\": 5551, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5447, \"end\": 5453, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Wagner\", \"score\": 0.9999995261588296, \"rank\": 4.738348174501332e-07, \"text\": \"Wagner\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Wagner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Wagner\"}, {\"begin\": 5484, \"end\": 5504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999996662154, \"rank\": 2.924643388372561e-10, \"text\": \"German national team\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 5510, \"end\": 5523, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dirk_Nowitzki\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dirk Nowitzki\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dirk_Nowitzki\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dirk_Nowitzki\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Wagner just signed a massive extension with the Orlando Magic, an extension that came after a career-low shooting season from beyond the arc - 28.1 percent on 334 attempts - and a dreadful 1-for-15, 6 point, performance in a Game 7 loss to the Cleveland Cavaliers in the first round of the playoffs.\", \"from\": 5553, \"to\": 5861, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5562, \"end\": 5568, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Wagner\", \"score\": 0.9999995261588296, \"rank\": 4.738348174501332e-07, \"text\": \"Wagner\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Wagner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Wagner\"}, {\"begin\": 5610, \"end\": 5623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Orlando_Magic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0514552188008915e-87, \"text\": \"Orlando Magic\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Orlando_Magic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Orlando_Magic\"}, {\"begin\": 5806, \"end\": 5825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleveland_Cavaliers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1967836574412813e-95, \"text\": \"Cleveland Cavaliers\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleveland_Cavaliers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleveland_Cavaliers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wagner is only 22.\", \"from\": 5862, \"to\": 5880, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5862, \"end\": 5868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Wagner\", \"score\": 0.9999995261588296, \"rank\": 4.738348174501332e-07, \"text\": \"Wagner\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Wagner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Wagner\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's got plenty of time to clear his name for the NBA playoffs and a strong showing at the Olympics could remind folks he has proven himself on big stages before.\", \"from\": 5881, \"to\": 6043, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5931, \"end\": 5934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.652738745170818e-61, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's certainly something Orlando Magic fans would like to see.\", \"from\": 6044, \"to\": 6106, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6069, \"end\": 6082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Orlando_Magic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0514552188008915e-87, \"text\": \"Orlando Magic\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Orlando_Magic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Orlando_Magic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Josh Giddey is still only 21 years old.\", \"from\": 6108, \"to\": 6147, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6108, \"end\": 6112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9765008641953165, \"rank\": 0.024064633442620165, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}, {\"begin\": 6113, \"end\": 6119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Giddey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Giddey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Giddey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Giddey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For a player who has been largely written off due to his status as the weakest link of the Oklahoma City Thunder in the 2024 NBA playoffs, that's pretty young.\", \"from\": 6148, \"to\": 6307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6239, \"end\": 6247, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oklahoma_Sooners_men's_basketball\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2424709868724778e-13, \"text\": \"Oklahoma\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oklahoma_Sooners_men's_basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oklahoma_Sooners_men's_basketball\"}, {\"begin\": 6273, \"end\": 6276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.652738745170818e-61, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Age aside, Giddey deserves the ire he's drawn.\", \"from\": 6308, \"to\": 6354, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6319, \"end\": 6325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Giddey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Giddey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Giddey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Giddey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is, for what is a somewhat lazy comparison, heading down a Ben Simmons path.\", \"from\": 6355, \"to\": 6434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6417, \"end\": 6428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Simmons\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ben Simmons\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Simmons\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Simmons\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was very impressive out of the gate as a rookie and sophomore, defying expectations, and then quickly being exposed as he reached the higher levels of the league due to his inability to improve on key elements of his game, primarily shooting and scoring.\", \"from\": 6435, \"to\": 6692, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Giddey was traded to the Chicago Bulls this offseason, straight-up, for Alex Caruso.\", \"from\": 6694, \"to\": 6778, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6694, \"end\": 6700, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Giddey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Giddey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Giddey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Giddey\"}, {\"begin\": 6719, \"end\": 6732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago_Bulls\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9100554056030147e-89, \"text\": \"Chicago Bulls\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago_Bulls\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago_Bulls\"}, {\"begin\": 6766, \"end\": 6777, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Caruso\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alex Caruso\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Caruso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Caruso\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This move has been widely perceived as a losing trade for the Bulls, who received no draft assets in return for the highly-coveted Caruso, who was apparently worth two first-round picks at the 2024 NBA trade deadline.\", \"from\": 6779, \"to\": 6996, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6910, \"end\": 6916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enrico_Caruso\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7758543195154197e-13, \"text\": \"Caruso\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enrico_Caruso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enrico_Caruso\"}, {\"begin\": 6977, \"end\": 6980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.652738745170818e-61, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The only way this trade turns into a win for the Bulls, and potentially saves general manager Arturas Karnisovas' job, is by Giddey getting better, developing more offensive and scoring verve, and taking his game to another level.\", \"from\": 6998, \"to\": 7228, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7123, \"end\": 7129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Giddey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Giddey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Giddey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Giddey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Regardless of what we saw happen in the 2024 NBA playoffs, he is still only 21, and has time to get better.\", \"from\": 7229, \"to\": 7336, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7274, \"end\": 7277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.652738745170818e-61, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics could serve as a testing ground for that.\", \"from\": 7337, \"to\": 7391, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Someone has to take the torch from Patty Mills and Matthew Dellavedova.\", \"from\": 7392, \"to\": 7463, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7427, \"end\": 7438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_Mills\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Patty 